- *         PassFailJFrame.positionTestWindow(testUI, PassFailJFrame.Position.HORIZONTAL);
- *         testUI.setVisible(true);
- *     }
- * }
- * }</pre>
- * <p>
- * Use methods of the {@code Builder} class or constructors of the
